Message: Koodo: Welcome to the U.S.! All incoming texts are FREE! Roaming rates without a U.S. roaming add-on: Voice=$1.50/min, Data=$5/20 MB TEXT=$5/100 outgoing texts.

Koodo: Welcome to the U.S.! All incoming texts are free. If you don't have a U.S. Roaming Add-on, the rates are Voice = $1.50/min, Data = $5 for every 20 MB used, Outgoing Text = $5 for every 100 text sent. For help, dial *611 or 16477884337.  Safe travels!
